<br>
Customs services have been expanded upon after the Sept 11 horse has bolted but only within the limited confines of the budget available. More money is needed. Policing import/export material and personal shipments should be a priority. Where will the money come from? Redirect impossible policing programs overseas. Before its too late.<br>
<br>
